text = "[center][font_size=44]How to Play[/font_size][/center]

[font_size=28]Goal[/font_size]
Explore the abandoned hospital and find all 5 pages hidden around the building. Collect all of them to escape.

[font_size=28]Controls[/font_size]
WASD — Move
Left Shift — Sprint
Mouse — Look around
Space — Jump
E — Interact (open/close doors, pick up pages and batteries)
1 — Hold the flashlight
2 — Hold the camcorder
Right Mouse — Raise/lower the camcorder
Esc — Pause menu

[font_size=28]Something is hunting you[/font_size]
You can't see it with your own eyes — it only shows up on the camcorder's screen. Raise the camcorder and point it at the entity to scare it off. Filming drains the camcorder's battery, so use it wisely and grab spare batteries when you find them lying around.

Good luck."
fit_content = false
scroll_active = true
